data.description: Welcome to your future oasis! This stunning property features 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 beautifully appointed bathrooms, ensuring both comfort and functionality for your family. With a generous 3-car garage, parking is a breeze, providing ample space for vehicles, storage, or even a workshop. New roof and solar panels installed in 2023. Situated on a lush .39-acre lot in the esteemed Sterling Hill community, this home offers a perfect blend of privacy and convenience. Low HOA fees and CDD included in taxes make for worry-free living, allowing you to enjoy all the amenities this community has to offer without breaking the bank. Step inside to discover a modern kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances for culinary enthusiasts and entertainers alike. Relax and unwind in the screened patio, surrounded by the serenity of a fully fenced vinyl yard, offering both privacy and security for outdoor gatherings or quiet evenings under the stars. This home features a thoughtful mix of vinyl, carpet, and tile flooring, providing both durability and style throughout. Plus, with an inside laundry room, chores become a breeze, adding to the convenience of everyday living. Don't miss your chance to make this your forever home – schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of comfortable, contemporary living!
